message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Finally, I've been waiting forever. I need to make a claim for my car accident.
I'm sorry to hear about your accident. Before we proceed, for GDPR purposes can you confirm your full name, date of birth, first line of address and postcode, and email address?
Ugh, fine. It's Sarah Johnson, 25th May 1985, 123 Green Street, AB12 3CD, sarah.johnson@email.com.
Thank you for completing security. I appreciate your patience. How can I assist you with your car accident claim today?
I just want to get this claim sorted quickly. It's been a nightmare.
I completely understand how important this is for you. Let me take a look and see what we can do. One possible resolution could be expediting the claim process for you. Would that work for you?
Yes, that would be great. I need this sorted out as soon as possible.
Perfect. I will make sure we prioritize your claim and get this sorted out swiftly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Just get this claim sorted, please.
Absolutely, Sarah. We will do our best to assist you. Thank you for reaching out to us. If you need further support, don't hesitate to contact us. Have a great day!
